88
00:06:36,660 --> 00:06:41,420
Mr. Ono, an editor at Shokabo who appears in the video

89
00:06:41,940 --> 00:06:45,380
said that when he was a young employee answering the company phone

90
00:06:46,100 --> 00:06:50,080
