93
00:06:57,840 --> 00:07:02,000
So why does this table of contents remain?

94
00:07:03,160 --> 00:07:05,780
This mystery is revealed in the video

95
00:07:06,760 --> 00:07:12,480
Editor Ono shares the story of his last meeting with Professor Imai

96
00:07:13,660 --> 00:07:17,720
Mr. Ono visited Professor Imai's home many times

97
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:22,279
asking "How is the manuscript for Volume 2 coming along?"

98
00:07:23,240 --> 00:07:26,800
Professor Imai was already in his 80s at that time

99
00:07:27,370 --> 00:07:30,520
