100
00:07:31,180 --> 00:07:35,660
Yet Mr. Ono had to follow up on the manuscript as part of his job

101
00:07:35,780 --> 00:07:38,220
You can feel his difficulty in doing so

102
00:07:39,640 --> 00:07:43,340
And the last time Mr. Ono met Professor Imai

103
00:07:44,060 --> 00:07:45,900
